      "sc:description": "Compilation of all names of Bacteria and Archaea which have been validly published according to the Bacteriological Code since 1 January 1980, and nomenclatural proposals that have been validly published since then. Was merged with LPSN and replaced by the new LPSN when LPSN was taken over by DSMZ.",
